"{\"uid\": \"si.com-fannation-boxing-samoan-boxing-coach-s-legacy-shines-at-paris-olympics-01j3w9gdw5xg\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"By Mohamed Bahaa  The boxing community is mourning the loss of Lionel Elika Fatupaito, the esteemed national boxing coach of Samoa, who tragically passed away at the Paris 2024 Olympics.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 186, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 70, \"end\": 75, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prince_of_Persia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Elika\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prince_of_Persia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prince_of_Persia\"}, {\"begin\": 125, \"end\": 130, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samoa\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.0673101946577943e-18, \"text\": \"Samoa\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samoa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samoa\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The International Boxing Association (IBA) announced his death on Saturday, revealing that Fatupaito, aged 60, died in the Olympic Village on Friday, just before the Opening Ceremony.\", \"from\": 187, \"to\": 370, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 191, \"end\": 223, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_International_Boxing_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.734555770741957e-20, \"text\": \"International Boxing Association\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_International_Boxing_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_International_Boxing_Association\"}, {\"begin\": 225, \"end\": 228, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"score\": 0.9993099106373415, \"rank\": 0.0006664415080263808, \"text\": \"IBA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\"}, {\"begin\": 310, \"end\": 325, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"score\": 0.9999999999972715, \"rank\": 2.550417096787533e-12, \"text\": \"Olympic Village\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\"}, {\"begin\": 353, \"end\": 369, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games_ceremony\", \"score\": 0.9650478970374575, \"rank\": 0.020049345444754573, \"text\": \"Opening Ceremony\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games_ceremony\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games_ceremony\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Fatupaito\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s passing has sent ripples of sorrow throughout the sporting world, with the IBA extending their \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cheartfelt condolences\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d to his family, friends, and the entire Samoan team.\", \"from\": 372, \"to\": 560, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 461, \"end\": 464, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"score\": 0.9993099106373415, \"rank\": 0.0006664415080263808, \"text\": \"IBA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\"}, {\"begin\": 484, \"end\": 493, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Heartfelt_(Kyla_album)\", \"score\": 0.9382360940984357, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"heartfelt\", \"types\": [\"Q482994\", \"Q386724\", \"Q2188189\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Heartfelt_(Kyla_album)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Heartfelt_(Kyla_album)\"}, {\"begin\": 548, \"end\": 554, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samoa\", \"score\": 0.9999999524152383, \"rank\": 4.7535581039309646e-08, \"text\": \"Samoan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samoa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samoa\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Lionel\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s dedication and passion for the sport have left an indelible mark on the boxing community,\\\" the IBA's statement read.\", \"from\": 561, \"to\": 689, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 668, \"end\": 671, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"score\": 0.9993099106373415, \"rank\": 0.0006664415080263808, \"text\": \"IBA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"His legacy will continue to inspire future generations.\", \"from\": 690, \"to\": 746, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Our thoughts and prayers are with Team Samoa and all those affected by this profound loss.\\\"\", \"from\": 747, \"to\": 838, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 786, \"end\": 791, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samoa\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.0673101946577943e-18, \"text\": \"Samoa\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samoa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samoa\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Pauga Talalelei Pauga, the President of the Samoan Olympic Committee, expressed the deep impact of Fatupaito\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s death, stating, \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cOur thoughts and those of the entire Samoan sporting community are with Lionel\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s family, his boxers, and friends.\", \"from\": 840, \"to\": 1087, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 884, \"end\": 890, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samoa\", \"score\": 0.9999999524152383, \"rank\": 4.7535581039309646e-08, \"text\": \"Samoan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samoa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samoa\"}, {\"begin\": 1009, \"end\": 1015, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samoa\", \"score\": 0.9999999524152383, \"rank\": 4.7535581039309646e-08, \"text\": \"Samoan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samoa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samoa\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He will be greatly missed.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d In a testament to his influence, Pauga and SASNOC Secretary General Maureen Tuimalealiifano gathered with the Samoan delegation for a briefing and a heartfelt team prayer, highlighting the emotional support extended to those closest to Fatupaito.\", \"from\": 1088, \"to\": 1364, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1186, \"end\": 1209, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maureen_Tuimalealiifano\", \"score\": 0.99999863793666, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Maureen Tuimalealiifano\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maureen_Tuimalealiifano\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maureen_Tuimalealiifano\"}, {\"begin\": 1228, \"end\": 1234, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samoa\", \"score\": 0.9999999524152383, \"rank\": 4.7535581039309646e-08, \"text\": \"Samoan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samoa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samoa\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ato Plodzicki-Faoagali, Samoa\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s sole boxer at the Games and a heavyweight contender, paid tribute to Fatupaito on Facebook.\", \"from\": 1366, \"to\": 1491, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"He was a kind and generous coach, not only with his time and material things but also his knowledge,\\\" Plodzicki-Faoagali reflected.\", \"from\": 1492, \"to\": 1624, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He recalled meeting Fatupaito when he was just 15, trialing for Samoa\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s youth team.\", \"from\": 1625, \"to\": 1710, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cYour dream was to attend an Olympics with me and Dad.\", \"from\": 1711, \"to\": 1767, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1763, \"end\": 1766, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Revenge\", \"score\": 0.8912074849999551, \"rank\": 0.12207316122381504, \"text\": \"Dad\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Revenge\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Revenge\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now you\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099ve left too early; we haven\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t had our first fight at the Olympics like we planned!\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d he lamented, illustrating the coach\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s integral role in his journey.\", \"from\": 1768, \"to\": 1935, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Plodzicki-Faoagali, a two-time Pacific Games champion, is set to fight Belgium\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s Victor Schelstraete on Sunday.\", \"from\": 1937, \"to\": 2050, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"With high hopes for victory, Plodzicki-Faoagali is a favorite in the 92kg class and carries the weight of his coach\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s dreams and expectations into the ring.\", \"from\": 2051, \"to\": 2209, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As he prepares to compete, the memory of Fatupaito's guidance and unwavering belief in his athletes will undoubtedly serve as a source of strength.\", \"from\": 2210, \"to\": 2357, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Fatupaito\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s influence on Samoan boxing is undeniable.\", \"from\": 2359, \"to\": 2414, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2386, \"end\": 2392, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samoa\", \"score\": 0.9999999524152383, \"rank\": 4.7535581039309646e-08, \"text\": \"Samoan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samoa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samoa\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Known for his steadfast dedication and belief in the Olympic ideal, he left a legacy that will continue to motivate and inspire future generations.\", \"from\": 2415, \"to\": 2562, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"His presence will be sorely missed, but his spirit lives on in the athletes he coached and the countless lives he touched throughout his distinguished career.\", \"from\": 2563, \"to\": 2721, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Loading recommendations...\", \"from\": 2723, \"to\": 2749, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Please wait while we load personalized content recommendations    \\u00c2\\u00a9 2026ABG-SI LLC-SPORTS ILLUSTRATED IS A REGISTERED TRADEMARK OF ABG-SI LLC.\", \"from\": 2750, \"to\": 2893, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"- All Rights Reserved.\", \"from\": 2894, \"to\": 2916, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The content on this site is for entertainment and educational purposes only.\", \"from\": 2917, \"to\": 2993, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Betting and gambling content is intended for individuals 21+ and is based on individual commentators' opinions and not that of Sports Illustrated or its affiliates, licensees and related brands.\", \"from\": 2994, \"to\": 3188, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3121, \"end\": 3139, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sports_Illustrated\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.764198703609505e-18, \"text\": \"Sports Illustrated\", \"types\": [\"Q41298\", \"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sports_Illustrated\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sports_Illustrated\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"All picks and predictions are suggestions only and not a guarantee of success or profit.\", \"from\": 3189, \"to\": 3277, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If you or someone you know has a gambling problem, crisis counseling and referral services can be accessed by calling 1-800-GAMBLER.\", \"from\": 3278, \"to\": 3410, \"entities\": []}]}"